{"tid":1021584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本「胸圍分布圖」揭密　這4地區女孩平均E罩杯","createTime":"2019-02-14T10:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T12:17:25.000Z","uid":212399,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"19ef85282d29940cbb21c57ad413063d90cab7ac","tid":1021584,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:43:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3391/d3391383.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3391%2Fd3391383.jpg&h=68f62065&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲日本AV女優椎名空。（示意圖／記者季相儒攝）<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n日本最近做了一項研究，想了解出生地與環境的不同，是否會影響到女性的胸圍大小，調查結果以「胸圍分布圖」的方式呈現，讓人一目了然各地區女性的胸圍概況，其中千葉縣、神奈川縣、大阪府以及福岡縣的平均都有到「E罩杯」，是全國最「突出」的區域。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3896/3896211.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3896%2F3896211.jpg&h=6451bf9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲約有57%女性的平均都落在D罩杯。（圖／<a href=\"http://翻攝自news-postseven.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%BF%BB%E6%94%9D%E8%87%AAnews-postseven.com&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDiWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=cb050a9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">翻攝自news-postseven.com</a>）<br />\n日本知名化妝品牌Love Cosme自2012年開始就在調查女性胸圍尺寸，從各地區抽出49名18歲到60歲的女性，結果顯示地區不同，大小也會不一樣，佐賀縣、大分縣、京都府、福井縣、滋賀縣以及奈良縣這6個區域的女性胸圍最平，平均是B罩杯，其他地區則大多是C罩杯到D罩杯。<br />\n東京大學進一步研究發現，女性乳房大小和染色體的基因組合有關，但這說法目前尚未獲得科學證實。<br />\n此外，之前網路上還流傳「女生多按摩就會讓罩杯升級」的說法，日本節目為了驗證傳言，請來27歲的寫真女星安田七奈實測，她的胸圍是81公分、D罩杯，照著專家教的按摩手法持續實驗12天。<br />\n在完成1萬次按摩後，安田七奈的上胸圍變成82公分，下胸圍縮小成68.5公分，罩杯則是從D連升2個CUP變成F罩杯，驚人成長讓所有人驚訝不已，驗證了按摩的確有助於胸部變大。專家也指出，除了可以讓胸部長大外，按摩也能幫助女性發現胸部有沒有異常。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190214/1377960.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190214%2F1377960.htm&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDiWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=f3ee319a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190214/1377960.htm</a>"},{"pid":"cf2aafa0ef00b9dfd17482784b1b7b10151c9178","tid":1021584,"uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:45:01.000Z","msg":"點解日本特別多大波妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6add4e9aab2080223c04ef05f3f9b50a87a507","tid":1021584,"uid":50890,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:46:29.000Z","msg":"日本級數減兩級就差唔多"},{"pid":"730bf4e8cbfc0c6849f0d65de60f8bf56a9fc01f","tid":1021584,"uid":23221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:47:46.000Z","msg":"港女： AAAAAAAAAAAAA"},{"pid":"8c024b588bae25ba1639ccaaa5396afd8fe8abcb","tid":1021584,"uid":76216,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:48:50.000Z","msg":"日本e 先=香港b/c"},{"pid":"848770c5187008c95daebb6460b11f6a27356655","tid":1021584,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc6add4e9aab2080223c04ef05f3f9b50a87a507","tid":1021584,"uid":50890,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:46:29.000Z","msg":"日本級數減兩級就差唔多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:50:24.000Z","msg":"扮大cup<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d81a82dd1398833205c4842e2323d8a02b9dcaa5","tid":1021584,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T12:17:25.000Z","msg":"大阪府E，京都府B <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}